#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an3.110"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.110:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.110:0.2"
msgid "11. Sambodhavagga "
msgstr "11. Awakening "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.110:0.3"
msgid "110. Byāpannasutta "
msgstr "110. Fallen "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an3.110:1.1"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho anāthapiṇḍikaṃ gahapatiṃ bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "Seated to one side, the Buddha said to the householder Anāthapiṇḍika: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.110:1.2"
msgid "“citte, gahapati, byāpanne kāyakammampi byāpannaṃ hoti, vacīkammampi byāpannaṃ hoti, manokammampi byāpannaṃ hoti. "
msgstr "“Householder, when the mind is fallen, bodily, verbal, and mental deeds are fallen. "

msgctxt "an3.110:1.3"
msgid "Tassa byāpannakāyakammantassa byāpannavacīkammantassa byāpannamanokammantassa na bhaddakaṃ maraṇaṃ hoti, na bhaddikā kālakiriyā. "
msgstr "Someone whose deeds of body, speech, and mind are fallen will not have a good death. "

msgctxt "an3.110:1.4"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, gahapati, kūṭāgāre ducchanne kūṭampi byāpannaṃ hoti, gopānasiyopi byāpannā honti, bhittipi byāpannā hoti; "
msgstr "It’s like a bungalow with a bad roof. The roof peak, rafters, and walls fall in. "

msgctxt "an3.110:1.5"
msgid "evamevaṃ kho, gahapati, citte byāpanne kāyakammampi byāpannaṃ hoti, vacīkammampi byāpannaṃ hoti, manokammampi byāpannaṃ hoti. "
msgstr "In the same way, when the mind is fallen, bodily, verbal, and mental deeds are fallen. "

msgctxt "an3.110:1.6"
msgid "Tassa byāpannakāyakammantassa byāpannavacīkammantassa byāpannamanokammantassa na bhaddakaṃ maraṇaṃ hoti, na bhaddikā kālakiriyā. "
msgstr "Someone whose deeds of body, speech, and mind are fallen will not have a good death. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli1.263, sc2
msgctxt "an3.110:2.1"
msgid "Citte, gahapati, abyāpanne kāyakammampi abyāpannaṃ hoti, vacīkammampi abyāpannaṃ hoti, manokammampi abyāpannaṃ hoti. "
msgstr "When the mind is not fallen, bodily, verbal, and mental deeds are not fallen. "

msgctxt "an3.110:2.2"
msgid "Tassa abyāpannakāyakammantassa abyāpannavacīkammantassa abyāpannamanokammantassa bhaddakaṃ maraṇaṃ hoti, bhaddikā kālakiriyā. "
msgstr "Someone whose deeds of body, speech, and mind are not fallen will have a good death. "

msgctxt "an3.110:2.3"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, gahapati, kūṭāgāre succhanne kūṭampi abyāpannaṃ hoti, gopānasiyopi abyāpannā honti, bhittipi abyāpannā hoti; "
msgstr "It’s like a bungalow with a good roof. The roof peak, rafters, and walls are not fallen in. "

msgctxt "an3.110:2.4"
msgid "evamevaṃ kho, gahapati, citte abyāpanne kāyakammampi abyāpannaṃ hoti, vacīkammampi abyāpannaṃ hoti, manokammampi abyāpannaṃ hoti. "
msgstr "In the same way, when the mind is not fallen, bodily, verbal, and mental deeds are not fallen. "

msgctxt "an3.110:2.5"
msgid "Tassa abyāpannakāyakammantassa … pe … abyāpannamanokammantassa bhaddakaṃ maraṇaṃ hoti, bhaddikā kālakiriyā”ti. "
msgstr "Someone whose deeds of body, speech, and mind are not fallen will have a good death.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.110:2.6"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

